net.sf.marineapi.nmea.sentence
Interface MWVSentence

All Superinterfaces:
Sentence
public interface MWVSentence
extends Sentence

Wind speed and angle. Speed in km/h, m/s, or knots. Wind angle is given in degrees relative to bow or true north.
